      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data (Hariharan et al. 2011) documents test conditions at five operating points. Flow rate uncertainty ±2%, speed uncertainty ±0.5 RPM, blood analogue viscosity ±3%. Temperature controlled to 37±0.5°C. MRL 2 requires Gradation 2; achieved Gradation 2."
