      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against experimental measurements at all 5 operating points. Agreement within combined uncertainty (simulation GCI 3.2% + experimental 8%) at 5/5 points. Maximum absolute error 6.4% at highest flow rate operating point. MRL 2 requires Gradation 2; achieved Gradation 2."
