    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Grid convergence confirmed (GCI 3.2%), output comparison within uncertainty at all 5 operating points, and validation scenario directly relevant to CPB COU. Relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) satisfied. Model credibility is sufficient to support worst-case hemolysis operating condition identification for the Class II CPB device.",
